Row 6: (implied) T26 holds {a0, a1, a2, a3}
Row 7: T27 holds {a0, a1, a2, a3}

MMA COMPUTATION 4
Matrix rows 0-7, Threads T12-T15 (rows 0-3) and T28-T31 (rows 4-7)

Row 0: T12 holds {a0, a1, a2, a3}
Row 1: (implied by arrow) T13 holds {a0, a1, a2, a3}
Row 2: (implied) T14 holds {a0, a1, a2, a3}
